=== 冰島 ===
{{Main|冰岛的可再生能源}}

[[冰島|冰島]]因為有地熱能所以20世紀以來一直是低碳經濟體. 但是國民所得提高後人均排放量有增加趨勢. 2009年統計[[冰島|冰島]]的地熱能和水力已經從90年代至今持續提供全島70%熱能和99%電力.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.statice.is/Uploads/files/LH06/L060701.xls |title=Gross energy consumption by source 1987–2005 |publisher=''[http://www.statice.is/?PageID=583 Statistics Iceland]'' |accessdate=2007-05-14 |format=XLS |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071125021947/http://www.statice.is/Uploads/files/LH06/L060701.xls |archivedate=2007-11-25 }}</ref> 因此雖使用很多一次性能源但人均排放量比美國低62%之多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mdgs.un.org/unsd/mdg/Data.aspx |title=United Nations Millennium Development Goals Indicators |publisher=[[United_Nations|United Nations]] |accessdate=2006-08-02 |archive-date=2011-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110317081247/http://mdgs.un.org/unsd/mdg/Data.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |url=http://eng.idnadarraduneyti.is/Publications/nr/1170 |title=Energy in Iceland |publisher=Icelandic Ministries of Industry and Commerce |accessdate=2007-05-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070305070726/http://eng.idnadarraduneyti.is/Publications/nr/1170 |archivedate=2007-03-05 }}</ref>,且因為都是[[可再生能源|可再生能源]]所以幾乎零成本. 冰島希望儘快達成100% 零排放並於2050 年達成[[氫經濟|氫經濟]] 目標.

